Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's why I'm thinking about\Nreading these creepy otaku novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, little girl.\NYou try saying that one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You just said "creepy otaku novels" while\Nf-facing the mistress of the light-novel section.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, creepy otaku novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Calm down, Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the combat tribes\Nfrom Adachi Ward!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you get it now, but stop calling novels\Nwith illustrations "creepy otaku novels".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, what should I call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Light-novel" is acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, "light-novel", is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you tell me which ones to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to like the stuff Izumi-chan likes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mune-kun, a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I get the gist of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I can not forgive her\Nfor the offensive language she spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You "can not"?\NWhat are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make her super-addicted\Nto light-novels and completely convert her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dear customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it? You can just call me Megumin,\Nlike most normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, Megumin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're looking for an entry-level\Nlight-novel, start with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}And I also recommend this one, and that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This many?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, more than anything else, this title!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Legend of the Illusionary Demon Sword," from\Nthe super-popular Senju Muramasa-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Our best-seller, and the second season\Nof the anime is on air right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, Megumin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? Tomorrow?
