Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, what's the meaning of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The novels you guys recommended\Nthe other day all ended at really good parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When are the sequels coming out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who knows? I've been waiting\Nfor the sequels for a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, you're an author, right? You can\Nspeak directly to the other authors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell them to stop playing hooky\Nand to hurry up and write the sequels!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't ask for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What should I do\Nwith this feeling of dissatisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}To lessen those symptoms,\Nyou just have to read other interesting books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, you achieved your goal, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wanted to start reading light-novels\Nto get common ground to talk to Sagiri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've gotten to like light-novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, I said you have to read\Nother interesting novels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How about borrowing one from Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wouldn't that be a better icebreaker\Nfor you to become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But would Izumi-chan see me\Nwith that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, for now, I'll try convincing her,\Nbut if it doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll cross that bridge when we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll drop by tomorrow after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the way, Megumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,did you already read\N"Silverwolf of Reincarnation" that I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was a bit iffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I have to talk to you.\NCan you open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san. What do you need to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, um, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you find someone who's cute, well-endowed,\Nand might be willing to show her panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it's not about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Megumi said she's coming by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- I'm heading over there now.\N- Okay, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I absolutely don't want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't say that.\NMegumi is a pretty good kid at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}She said she wanted\Nto like the stuff you like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a cute dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't it okay to lend her a few books?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's lend her "Maria-sama ga Miteru"\Nseries except for "Putting Up the Parasol".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How do you come up\Nwith such devilish thoughts, Nii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In any case, I don't want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it's just lending books... Then, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But, I-I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One condition? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The class rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...is cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello! It's Megumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As the condition for lending me books,\NI need to be a model for her drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri says she's fine seeing you\Nif that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She wants to draw using me as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I may have something here with Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Perhaps so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was an amateur model\Nfor a magazine one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm okay with any pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what should I do from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-chan won't come out of her room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing less from a magazine model.\NYou look good no matter what you wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. Sagiri said\Nyou have to be in that state for her to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll call for Sagiri now. But you have\Nto promise not take the blindfold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How am I going to do that in this state?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I brought her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I blindfolded her, and made her immobile.\NNothing to be scared of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.\NTo think she'd let her in here so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um, Izumi-chan, you're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not getting a reply from Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm getting super uneasy, like some\Nlewd punishment is going to begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like you to refrain from vulgar comments\Nin front of my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri is concentrating on drawing,\Nso she can't respond to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G-Gazes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lewd gazes on my thighs and boobs\Nare making my neck and spine tingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've been acting\Nstrangely bashful for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. As if you're not used to having\Nlewd gazes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Perhaps you think being a slut is fashionable?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're just putting on airs\Nand pretending to be a lewd girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong!\NI... well, have lots of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've seen a penis before, too!
