Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cute striped panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are we going to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought it would be bad,\Nbut I couldn't hold in my urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}So you can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Izumi-chan, you can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With me! Without blindfolds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's not all right... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're already friends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since you've already seen my panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So horrible! You even took my panties off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not even my little brother has seen them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said you'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I said that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't there something else you can say?\NLike, a friendship has been born?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, "Thank you for the meal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's time for you to pay up!\N- Pay up? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Being a friend is impossible,\Nbut this is the reward you were promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. That's what we promised, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, my favorite books...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,These are the books Izumi-chan likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. My most favorite books\Nin the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll get to liking these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I'm done reading them,\Ncan you lend me other books?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well then, that's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, and can you give me back\Nmy panties that you put in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Please wait until I'm done\Nwith my illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.58,OnTop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz333.8\pos(73.549,283.888)}Matilda\N-First Year Junior High Student\N-Blood Type O\N-A girl who's always copying\Nthe Protagonist's younger sister\N-Returning to Japan,\Na half-Japanese and\Nhalf-Netherlands girl\N-The younger sister said\Nthey can become friends\Nif Matilda shows her panties\Nto her, so she does
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.21,OnTop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.7,47.444)}Sayaka\N-Second Year Junior High Student\N-Blood Type AB\N-Protagonist's younger sister's friend\Nfrom school\N-When she went into\Nthe younger sister's room,\Nthe younger sister tied her up\Nand blindfolded her\N-She gets her striped panties\Ntaken from her, but their friendship\Ngrows from there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, let's go with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's do our best for publication next May!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a year from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I had secured a publishing spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but right after that message, a popular author\Nbrought in manuscripts for a new title,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so that one took priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That popular author is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The young ace of our label, Muramasa-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa? Her again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, you're unemployed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah. It's the same as two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Back then, after overcoming multiple no-gos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}a proposal for a new title\Nfinally went through, and she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Senju Muramasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's the author for\NLegend of the Illusionary Demon Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah. Super-duper popular compared to me,\Nand is a lot like me in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A lot like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First of all, our pennames are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The writing style is completely the same, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Battle stuff with a splash of Japanese tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, that really is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's supposedly a fast writer,\Nand a student author who is younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...an upgrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I got that a lot when I first debuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Fake Muramasa-sensei", "a degradation\Nof Muramasa", "horrible even for a follower"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dammit, Masamune is stronger\Nin Final Fantasy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're being too unsightly. Please shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a shame the release date\Nwill be far off in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, they'll turn it into a book next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, we've moved one step forward.\NCongratulations, Izumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei...\NUnfortunately, that's not really the case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you in money trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If so, I can provide for you, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll draw l-lewd illustrations and make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}An older brother who makes his younger sister\Nprovide for him by drawing lewd illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, I drew a lewd illustration.\NIf we sell this, we can live for another month!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}N-No, I'm really happy you're offering,\Nbut hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I'm worried about is not simply\Nbeing in a financial bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I made a promise with our aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}As long as I can regularly show results\Nas an author,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}then she'll allow us to continue\Nour "current way of life".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, if I don't publish any books\Nfor a whole year, I'd be breaking that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about getting the book out sooner\Nfrom another publisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It would be nice if I could, but I don't\Nknow anyone in other publishing companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. I didn't think your older brother\Nwas the editor in charge of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But my older brother is so square-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before seeing the project proposal, he asked us\Nto first clear it with your editorial staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks like we got here\Nearlier than the appointment time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I know! Let's stop by a café!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You must have thought,\N"This is almost like a date," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a date or anything at all,\Nbut I'll specially allow you to fantasize that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:21.88,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(510.333,177.778)\frz334.6}Yamada Elf on a date with Izumi Masamune-sensei right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.12,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(483.833,257.778)\frx0\fry0\frz336.3}Submitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:23.24,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frx0\fry0\frz353.8\pos(439.017,261.333)}Submitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:23.35,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frx0\fry0\frz9.068\pos(383.367,283.555)}Submitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:23.48,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(426.65,394.666)\frz20\frx354\fry356}Submitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder how big the sales\Nfor the second anime season
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,of Legend of the Illusionary\NDemon Sword will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really do like talking about sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't it fun to compare your sales\Nto other authors, and see if you won or lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you the type who says, "It's embarrassing\Nto be conscious about sales" and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't understand that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're playing the most interesting\Ncompetitive game in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why aren't you looking at the scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're "the type who acts tsundere\Nto her readers," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Don't get me wrong!\NI'm only interested in sales and praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All my readers are my servants!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'm just putting some distance between\Nmyself and the readers as a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I like my readers or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,J-Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, great Elf-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you're losing in sales you love so much\Nagainst the aforementioned Muramasa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmph. It's useless to go against\Nsomeone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For instance, Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If a reader told you,\N"Elf-sensei's books were more interesting".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd be super disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-By love, I don't mean it that way, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just saying how winning against those
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,who get frustrated about it\Nlike you is the most amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Muramasa. She's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if I stomped her down in sales,\Nshe wouldn't be disappointed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's playing a one-player game\Nthat's different from what we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Crap, we're cutting it really close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's some outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you!\NDo you have business in this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geez, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Could this be a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah-hah! You must be a rookie\Nbringing in a piece for review!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this. Right now, no publisher will\Naccept pieces from people with no real results.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But since you came all the way here,\Nyou can tag along with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To make up for earlier, I'll ask them to at least\Ngive you a tour of the editorial department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I, Yamada Elf, will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know of me\Nif you're an aspiring author, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Yamada Elf, a popular author\Ntotaling over 2 million copies in print!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look here. I'm a popular author\Nwho will have a title turned into an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing not to know! Embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop that. She's troubled by all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, hush, combat power of 220 grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I sold 2 million copies,\Nso I can say whatever I want to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what it means to have more than\N1 million copies' worth of difference in sales!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.\NIt looks like she's in a bad mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I just heard something nice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, I read your e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to work with another publisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I called the other publisher\Nand properly settled things already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's keep at this three-legged race together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen,\Nso that's why I tagged along!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you were here, Yamada-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No matter what this old hag says,\Nyour choices haven't been crushed down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a dream that's more important\Nthan anything else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kagurazaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to publish the romantic comedy proposal\Nthat I submitted the other day, into a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This year, and the sooner the better. I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So please, give me some advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, you should listen to the very end\Nwhen someone's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't just turn me into a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been thinking of various ideas as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Light-novel Tenkaichi Budokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Light-novel Tenkaichi Budokai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A new project where five\Nup-and-coming authors publish short stories
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in a magazine,\Nand compete for a publishing spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The winning title will be sold\Nas a book form in September?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You technically can't enter unless\Nyou're a rookie author that just debuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I'll use my authority to push you in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words, if I win this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.41,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(507.034,265.333)\frx0\fry0\frz26.05}IZUMI MASAMUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi Masamune-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have accepted your entry\Nin the Light-novel Tenkaichi Budokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Please do your best!\N- I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I sought your advice,\NKagurazaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's still too early to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You won't get that publishing spot\Nunless you defeat four rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the first step towards our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi Masamune-kun,\Nyour dream will not come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I will not let it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your little sentimental dream\Nis in the way of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I will make sure to crush them right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.80,CenterSignM2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz339.2\move(443.433,290.667,435.483,293.334,1,459)}SENJU MURAMASA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senju...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senju Muramasa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not good to lack honorifics, kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You will call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Muramasa-senpai"!
